seo: 反defang,IP还原,URL还原,威胁情报处理
seo_en: anti-defang, IP restoration, URL restoration, threat intelligence processing
summary: 该插件用于将威胁情报中被defang的IP和URL还原为原始格式，例如将127[.]0[.]0[.]1还原为127.0.0.1。
summary_en: This plugin is used to restore defanged IPs and URLs in threat intelligence to their original format, e.g., restoring 127[.]0[.]0[.]1 to 127.0.0.1.
